Package energy.usef.agr.model.device.capability

Model classes of aggregator device capabilities.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DeviceCapability
    Abstract entity class representing the capability of a UDI device.
    IncreaseCapability
    Entity class for the increase capability of a UDI device.
    InterruptCapability
    Entity class representing an interrupt capability of a UDI device.
    ReduceCapability
    Entity class representing a reduce capability of a UDI device.
    ReportCapability
    Entity class representing a report capability of a UDI device.
    ShiftCapability
    Entity class representing a shift capability of a UDI device.
    VariationCapability
    Abstract entity representing a variation capability (increase or reduce) of a UDI device.

    Enumeration of the various InterruptCapability types.
